									<templateId root="2.16.840.1.113883.2.1.3.2.4.18.2" extension="COCD_TP146061UK02#section2"/>
									<text>
										Series of 6 chest images 27/2/07
										to 3/1/07
										<br/>
										The initial image shows a large
										(70%) right-sided pneumothorax
										with no evidence of mediastinal
										shift or other complications.
										The subsequent images show a
										chest drain in satisfactory
										position, with gradual
										resolution of the pneumothorax
										which is minimal by the last
										film on Sunday morning. No
										evidence of complications.

									</text>
									<title>Summary</title>
								</section2>
